linux-2.6 (3.1.0-1+grml.1) grml-testing; urgency=low

  * Grml build of 3.1.0.
  * Note that Grml builds are very vanilla.
  * Based on Debian kernel/dists/trunk/linux-2.6/debian rev 18236

