  * New upstream release: http://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_2_6_37
    - starfire: Fix dma_addr_t size test for MIPS (fixes FTBFS)
    - watchdog: Improve failure message and documentation (Closes: #608138)

  [ Ben Hutchings ]
