  * New upstream release: http://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_2_6_33

  [ maximilian attems]
  * [topconfig] set BLK_DEV_DRBD, DRM_NOUVEAU, DRM_NOUVEAU_BACKLIGHT,
    DRM_VMWGFX, SENSORS_LM73, SENSORS_AMC682, SENSORS_LIS3_I2C,
