    (closes: #278729)
  * Enable OBSOLETE_OSS_USB_DRIVER and USB_AUDIO
    as alsa snd-usb-audio still isn't quite there.
    I expect this to be re-disabled at some stage,
    possibly soon if it proves to be a source of bugs.
